{
  "stem": "27507.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we finally somehow moved into this apartment in-- probably in autumn, 1940.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandfather died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was my maternal grandfather, and that was a great shock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was great, great shock for everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was still not old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was maybe in his early 60s.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that must have happened, I think, around Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think what happened was that he went to his cousin, Hirsch Adler who-- whom I knew quite well was invited to for dinner and must have eaten too well and later, didn't feel well and had a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was-- of course, everybody was shocked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that must have been then in probably September or beginning of October 1940.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But in retrospect, it was quite lucky that it happened at this particular moment because it happened-- it was still in his own-- he was still brought to his flat.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it happened before any extreme measures were taken and before ghetto was formed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as he was-- and as he was very religious orthodox Jew, it's almost unthinkable that he would have survived.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he was buried on the-- in the cemetery in Powazki, in the cemetery in Powazki.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was a big funeral, which I don't-- I, I-- which I didn't go to.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so and then-- and that must have happened briefly before ghetto was-- before we went into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So when we moved-- I just try to think if there was anything else in this period, but it will come later.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was-- I think it was only us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was, of course, a-- and so anyway, the question was of moving into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
